title: The Mysterious Cities of Gold (AVI format)
description:
The Mysterious Cities of Gold, is a French-Japanese animated series co-produced by DIC Entertainment and Studio Pierrot. The series premiered in Japan on NHK on 29 June 1982 and ran weekly for 39 episodes until its conclusion on 7 June 1983.

I changed the original format to AVI because I didn't have anything on my computer that would play the original.
